# The Minotaur — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of The Minotaur](the-minotaur.png)

**what —** The bellowing warden of the Circle of Violence.

**why —** Rage and monstrousness made into a gatekeeper.

**how —** It gnaws itself in fury — and in its blind rage the travelers slip past.

**where —** The shattered cliff down into Circle VII.

